<h1>About</h1>

<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Welcome to <span style="color: #FF9900;">The Rule of Two Collectables</span>!
  </h1>
  <p style="text-align: justify;">
    We're your premier destination for a galaxy of collectibles. Explore our extensive selection of Star Wars action figures, featuring the iconic 3.75-inch and 6-inch renditions. Immerse yourself in the detailed world of Transformers with our Studio Series and Masterpiece editions. Embrace the heroics of GI Joe through our exclusive 6-inch Classified Series, and discover the vast universe of Marvel Legends.
